  1. Menu button random pastel color like menulinks and dummies
  2. info bubbles on single art view also falls in new Scene
  2.1. Scene complete remodel / refactor to make it stop interaction with "outside world" 
  2.2. Or: dedicated scene
  3. smooth color transitions on menu toggle

  BUGS
